        public void editProfile(java.lang.String name,

                 throws JSONException,

        this class takes in edited name, age,university, home and away city and puts the edited name, age, university, home and away into the user profile. The Http Client sends an HTTP PUT request to the API to update the name, age, university, home, away. The API sends information which is stored in Android via JSON to the webserver.
